How many casts and how much time is very relevant because you can use it along with the melees dps to figure out how much dmg you will take taking down a given melee and if you have enough hp/time to do it.  This doesn't take into acount the casts a wiz can get off while leved, around corners, through walls while a melee is trying to find you after a good ss and so on.<br>
