Take the 2nd log for example. First off you didn't cast your rune.  Assuming you will be in melee for 2.5 seconds out of every 4.5 second cast of lure of ice and kill the rogue on the 4th cast. Then assuming you will channel 1/2 the time.  You will be in melee for 5 seconds per cast or 20 seconds.  At 60dps this is 1200 dmg.  Even without your rune this wont kill you.  With it you will finish the rogue with an embarassing (for the rogue) 3 bars of hp remaining.  Without your rune he needs at least 72 dps.  With it he needs 110 dps or 72dps + whatever he needs to make up for the dmg he takes dispelling you.  In addition yondering, casting epic and attacking again is a good way to wear him down.<br>
